---
title: Grilled Chicken Breasts and Elotes-Inspired Salad with Grilled Sweet Potato Wedges
description: Head to the streets of Mexico with this lip-smacking BBQ recipe featuring perfectly-spiced chicken and elotes – grilled Mexican-style street corn! These corn on the cobs are coated in creamy feta, zesty lime and smoky spices, and offer a fun twist on the standard buttered version.
